<body><div>
<milestone unit="question" spanTo="#questionEnd"/>
<p><lb/>For <choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi></orig><reg>the</reg></choice> Lady Magdalen Egerton <lb/><choice><orig>I</orig><reg>J</reg></choice>une 30. <choice><orig>☉</orig><reg type="gloss">Sunday</reg></choice> h. 2. p. m. 1633.</p>
<anchor xml:id="questionEnd"/>
<milestone unit="recipe" spanTo="#recipeEnd1"/>
<p><lb/><foreign xml:lang="la">℞ Aloes Cicotrina ℥<choice><orig><seg rend="cardo">ß</seg></orig><reg>semis</reg><reg type="gloss">half</reg></choice>. Turbith, <lb/><foreign xml:lang="en">and</foreign> Agarick an. ʒi<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. Myrabolan<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice> <lb/>Chebulæ ʒi<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. Rubarb. ʒ<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. <del type="strikethrough"><unclear cert="low" reason="del">v</unclear></del> <lb/>Masticis calam<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice> aromatic<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice> an ʒ<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. <lb/>fiat Massa c<choice><orig>ū</orig><reg>um</reg></choice> syrupo viola<choice><orig>ꝝ</orig><reg>rum</reg></choice>. <lb/>in 5. pil.</foreign> dos. once in 2 dayes. <lb/>at 5. of clocke before Supper. <lb/>ad to it of p<unclear cert="low" reason="faded">ill</unclear> Rud ʒ<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>.</p>
<anchor xml:id="recipeEnd1"/>
<milestone unit="treatment" spanTo="#treatmentEnd1"/>
<p><lb/>A dry Diet Drinke to dry <lb/><choice><orig>v</orig><reg>u</reg></choice>p <choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi></orig><reg>the</reg></choice> Rheume. corroboratinge <lb/><choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi></orig><reg>the</reg></choice> Animall &amp; vitall <del type="strikethrough">spirits</del> Parts.</p>
<anchor xml:id="treatmentEnd1"/>
<milestone unit="recipe" spanTo="#recipeEnd2"/>
<p><lb/>Take <choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi></orig><reg>the</reg></choice> barke of lign<choice><orig>ū</orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <choice><orig>s<hi rend="overline">ct</hi>ū</orig><reg>sanctum</reg></choice>. sarsaperilla, sassafras. <lb/>roote, calamus Aromaticus of sach ℥ii<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. Sliced <lb/>cinamoms nuttmegs. &amp; galingall an. ℥<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice> sliced <lb/>Angelia canded, enula campana canded <lb/>myrabulo<unclear cert="low" reason="hand">u</unclear>s condited ℥i<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. Bisket Bred made <lb/>with anyseed ℥iii<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice> beaten &amp; pouderd. verven <lb/>&amp; Celandine. dryed an. ♏. i<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. wood bittony <lb/>Marger<choice><orig>ā</orig><reg>am</reg></choice>, &amp; rosemary flowers dryed <del type="strikethrough"><gap reason="del" extent="1" unit="chars"/>ac. ♏. ij.</del> <lb/>an ℥<choice><orig><seg rend="cardo">ß</seg></orig><reg>semis</reg><reg type="gloss">half</reg></choice>. Pruons ♏.<choice><orig><seg rend="cardo">ß</seg></orig><reg>semis</reg><reg type="gloss">half</reg></choice>. Licoras Aniseeds &amp; <lb/>reasons an. ℥v<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. flower de Luce roote <lb/>&amp; flag roote boath dryed &amp; sliced let all <lb/>these be boyled in 20 pints of spring water <lb/>boyle it till 4. pints be wasted then adde <lb/>to it Bittony water, Marger<choice><orig>ū</orig><reg>um</reg></choice> &amp; Rosemary waters <lb/>an. <hi rend="overline">lib.</hi> <choice><orig><seg rend="cardo">ß</seg></orig><reg>semis</reg><reg type="gloss">half</reg></choice> white wyne <hi rend="overline">lib</hi> i<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice> boyle it a little more <lb/>then strayne it &amp; stop it close in a sweet <choice><orig>I</orig><reg>J</reg></choice>ug pot.</p>
<anchor xml:id="recipeEnd2"/>
<milestone unit="treatment" spanTo="#treatmentEnd2"/>
<p><lb/>Take of this e<choice><orig>u</orig><reg>v</reg></choice>ery morneing ℥v<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. &amp; the like at <lb/>3. in <choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi></orig><reg>the</reg></choice> after noone &amp; supping with 3 slices of <lb/>Dyet bread drink ℥v<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. more &amp; so <choice><orig>v</orig><reg>u</reg></choice>se it as <lb/>long as any Lasteth.</p>
<p><lb/>Let her suppers be during this tyme of bisket bread &amp; reasons of <lb/><choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi></orig><reg>the</reg></choice> sunne. &amp; sometymes ponadoes, with a little bisket bread or 3. <lb/>slices of dyet bread. <add place="supralinear">&amp; may drinke after it her dyet drinke before p<choice><orig><hi rend="superscript">r</hi></orig><reg>re</reg></choice>scrib<supplied reason="binding" cert="high">ed</supplied></add> at other tymes either citrons, Lemons or <lb/>oringes Canded or condited &amp; once in 2 or 3 dayes to take <del type="strikethrough">before</del> <lb/>an houre before such a slight supper. 5. smal pils.</p>
<cb xml:id="colB" n="b"/>
<p><lb/>Aloes cicotr <add place="supralinear">ʒi<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice></add> <subst><del type="strikethrough">rud,</del> <add place="supralinear">Rud ℥<choice><orig><seg rend="cardo">ß</seg></orig><reg>semis</reg><reg type="gloss">half</reg></choice></add></subst> fætid <lb/>turb an ʒi<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. salis <lb/>g<choice><orig>ē</orig><reg>em</reg></choice>m ʒ<choice><orig><seg rend="cardo">ß</seg></orig><reg>semis</reg><reg type="gloss">half</reg></choice> fiat <lb/>mass pil c<choice><orig>ū</orig><reg>um</reg></choice> syr <lb/>de S rad q sup<gap extent="unclear" reason="binding"/> <lb/>dosis ʒ<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice></p>
<anchor xml:id="treatmentEnd2"/>
</div>
<div><pb xml:id="p511" n="511"/>
<milestone unit="recipe" spanTo="#recipeEnd3"/>
<head>The Electuary.</head>
<p><lb/>Take of wood Bittony, Dianthos <lb/>Conserve of <add place="supralinear">old</add> Red Roses, Condited <lb/>Citrons an. ℥<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. Ivory, harts horne <lb/>specier<choice><orig>ū</orig><reg>um</reg></choice> de ge<choice><orig>m̄</orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>is powderd an ʒ<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. <lb/>venice treacle ʒi<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. Trochiskes of <lb/>vipers. ʒ<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>. Let all be well mixed <lb/>&amp; incorporated with <choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi></orig><reg>the</reg></choice> syrupe <lb/>Acetositate citr<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice>.</p>
<anchor xml:id="recipeEnd3"/>
<milestone unit="treatment" spanTo="#treatmentEnd3"/>
<p><lb/>Dosis as much as a Nuttmeg <lb/>in <choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi></orig><reg>the</reg></choice> morneing fasting. &amp; then <lb/>p<choice><orig><hi rend="superscript">r</hi></orig><reg>re</reg></choice>sently drink after it ℥v<choice><orig>j</orig><reg>i</reg></choice> <lb/>of <choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi></orig><reg>the</reg></choice> former dyet drinke <lb/>puting into this draught <lb/>only in the morneinge <lb/>Syrup of Roses 2. Spoonfuls. <lb/>&amp; not in <choice><orig>y<hi rend="superscript">t</hi></orig><reg>that</reg></choice> in the afternoone.</p>
<anchor xml:id="treatmentEnd3"/>
</div>

